Oh another docker container I suggest you add is Watchtower, it manages your containers for you and prevents a buildup of cache on your SD card.

docker run -d \
  --name watchtower \
  --restart unless-stopped \
  -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock \
  containrrr/watchtower \
  --cleanup \
  --schedule 0 0 24 * * *
